---
// Our Story — Warren leads (green). Brand-sanctioned copy; the full
// narrative and real photography swap in later via the photo slot.
---

<section id="story" class="section story" data-lead="green" aria-labelledby="story-title">
  <div class="container story__grid">
    <div class="story__copy" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p>
      <h2 id="story-title" class="story__title">Nine years, and a great many dinners</h2>
      <p class="story__lede">
        After nine years, one very persistent cat, and a great many dinners, we are
        overjoyed to gather the people we love — and to begin the next of those nine years
        in front of you.
      </p>
      <p class="story__body">
        We met long before we knew where it would lead, and we have been writing the story
        ever since. There is far more of it than fits here: how we met, the question and the
        answer, and the cat who considers herself a third party to this engagement.
      </p>
      <a class="gg-link story__more" href="#story">Read how it happened</a>
    </div>

    <figure class="story__figure" data-reveal>
      <div class="photo-slot">
        <figcaption class="photo-slot__caption">
          <span class="mark" aria-hidden="true">&#10022;</span>
          Warren &amp; Carson
        </figcaption>
      </div>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.15fr) minmax(0, 0.85fr);
    gap: clamp(var(--space-6), 6vw, var(--space-9));
    align-items: center;
  }
  .story__copy { max-width: 56ch; }
  .story__title { margin-bottom: var(--space-5); }
  .story__lede {
    font-size: var(--fs-body-lg);
    color: var(--parchment-200);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .story__body { color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 60ch; }
  .story__more {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    font-family: var(--font-deco);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-label);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--lead-strong);
  }
  .story__more::after { background: var(--lead); }

  .story__figure { margin: 0; }
  .story__figure .photo-slot { box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .story__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-7); }
    .story__figure { max-width: 420px; margin-inline: auto; order: -1; }
    .story__copy { max-width: none; }
  }
</style>
